<div class="text-center" style="padding-top:50px;">
    <b style="font-size:20px">Feeling of a sense of purpose is just a few clicks away!</b>
</div>

<div style="padding-top:50px;">
    <div class="card">
        <button id="button" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("PreferenceCheck", "Jobs")'">Volunteer Search</button>
        <div>
            <p id="paragraph">Make a difference in the community by donating your time to educate those in need.</p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <button id="button" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("Test", "Home")'">Infographics</button>
        <div>
            <p id="paragraph">Our comprehensive information page will help you to understand the disparity between the rich and poor.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <button id="button" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("Test", "Home")'">Aptitude Quiz</button>
        <div>
            <p id="paragraph">Take a quiz to see what opportunities best suit you and how you can contribute to the fight!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <style>
        .card {
            text-align: center;
            width: 25%;
            height: 250px;
            float: left;
            margin-left: 80px;
            margin-right: auto;
            background-color:lightyellow;
            border-radius: 25px;
        }

        #paragraph {
            padding-top: 30px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        #button {
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            background-color: #C2EDCE;
            font-size:20px;
            font-weight:bold;
        }

        #button:hover {
            background-color: #3e8e41
        }

        #button:active {
            background-color: #3e8e41;
            box-shadow: 0 5px #666;
            transform: translateY(4px);
        }
    </style>
</div>
